OL,3,CChildren's ambulance transforming how
OL,4,Cyoung patients travel for cardiac care
OL,6,FA specially designed, life-saving
OL,7,Fchildren's ambulance is playing a
OL,8,Fvital role in transporting young
OL,9,Fpatients in Northern Ireland who
OL,10,Frequire specialist cardiac care.
OL,12,FThe bespoke vehicle is central to
OL,13,Fbringing children to and from Dublin
OL,14,Ffor treatment and, at this time of
OL,15,Fyear, is also used to transfer sick
OL,16,Fchildren to hospitals closer to home,
OL,17,Fhelping them stay nearer to their
OL,18,Ffamilies.
