OL,3,CChildren's ambulance transforming how
OL,4,Cyoung patients travel for cardiac care
OL,6,FOperated by the Northern Ireland
OL,7,FSpecialist Transport and Retrieval
OL,8,F(NISTAR) team, the ambulance forms
OL,9,Fpart of Northern Ireland's critical
OL,10,Fcare transfer service for adult,
OL,11,Fpediatric and neonatal patients.
OL,13,FSince entering service in 2023, it has
OL,14,Falready completed hundreds of
OL,15,Fjourneys, with ongoing support from
OL,16,Fthe Children's Heartbeat Trust.
