OL,3,CChildren's ambulance transforming how
OL,4,Cyoung patients travel for cardiac care
OL,6,FThe ambulance was commissioned
OL,7,Ffollowing a hugely successful 'Mile A
OL,8,FDay' fundraising campaign in 2021,
OL,9,Fwhich raised more than #100,000 from
OL,10,Fthe public. The Children's Heartbeat
OL,11,FTrust donated #100,000 towards the
OL,12,F#140,000 cost of building the bespoke
OL,13,Fvehicle, working in partnership with
OL,14,Fthe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,15,F(NIAS).
