OL,3,CChildren's ambulance transforming how
OL,4,Cyoung patients travel for cardiac care
OL,6,FThe aim was clear, to create a
OL,7,Fwelcoming and comforting space for
OL,8,Fchildren and their families at a time
OL,9,Fwhen anxiety can be at its highest.
OL,10,FDuring the festive season in
OL,11,Fparticular, the ambulance plays a
OL,12,Fcrucial role in transferring children
OL,13,Fto their local hospital, helping them
OL,14,Fremain close to loved ones while also
OL,15,Fsupporting bed management at the Royal
OL,16,FBelfast Hospital for Sick Children.
