OL,3,CChildren's ambulance transforming how
OL,4,Cyoung patients travel for cardiac care
OL,6,FAlongside medical equipment, the
OL,7,Fdedicated children's ambulance
OL,8,Ffeatures space-themed interior decor,
OL,9,Fsensory equipment designed to calm
OL,10,Fyounger patients, and PlayStation and
OL,11,Ftablet facilities to help entertain
OL,12,Fchildren during long journeys. It is
OL,13,Falso adapted with wheelchair tracks,
OL,14,Fallowing older children to travel in
OL,15,Ftheir own wheelchair rather than on a
OL,16,Ftrolley.
