OL,3,CChildren's ambulance transforming how
OL,4,Cyoung patients travel for cardiac care
OL,6,FFive-year-old Reuben Kirkpatrick from
OL,7,FCookstown, who was born with a heart
OL,8,Fdefect, has travelled between Dublin
OL,9,Fand the Royal Victoria Hospital in the
OL,10,FChildren's Ambulance for open-heart
OL,11,Fsurgery.
OL,13,FHis mum, Roberta Donnelly, said the
OL,14,Fexperience has made a difficult
OL,15,Fjourney much easier for both of them.
